                                    {
                                      "text": "Kitchen Hide-and-Seek is a fun hide-and-seek minigame taking place in a huge kitchen. Some of the hiding places include a large fridge, cupboards, a zink and an oven. It looks quite realistic and it will feel as if you are an ant in a huge world. \n If you don\u2019t know how to play hide-and-seek, make sure to read the instructions further down on this page. \n The seeker should jump into the cobweb and wait to pass through (don\u2019t break the cobweb). Once the seeker has passed through the cobweb he or she can start looking for other players. Found players should announce in the chat that they have been found and gather back at the starting area.", 
